- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as spreadsheets are a form of programming language and the paper may discuss the syntax and semantics of spreadsheet documentation.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper may discuss how documentation can improve the usability and accessibility of spreadsheets for users.
- cs.DB (Databases) is a possible category as spreadsheets can be used as a simple form of database and the paper may discuss how documentation can improve data management.
- cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) is the least likely category as there is no indication that the paper discusses security or cryptography in spreadsheets.
